{"tid":369932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"魔鬼胸 蔚X芯 偽人真面目!","createTime":"2017-08-22T16:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T14:51:56.000Z","uid":101454,"like":10,"dislike":1173,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f734bc94748eac8daf6e7edcb5a6d6e9606b6fc7","tid":369932,"uid":101454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:40:56.000Z","msg":"請大家評下道理？<br />\n<br />\n事源於15-8-17 藝人蔚X芯，原名姓劉X麗，當日同经理人经我同我同事参觀荃城匯，表示有興趣3房，因當時未能可能正式登记，故稍后才辦，之后一路有同我同事联络关於按揭事情，而當中亦有提及回佣事情，但當時發展商未正式公佈正确佣金，故经纪口頭上已经答应没問題，但要待發展商公佈正确佣金后才作實，以便大家有誤会，直至上星期四已经可以正式登记入票，我同事便联络她什么时候方便來登记，她説星期五六不在香港，回来后可以登记，而到今日星期一，收到风她已经经其他经纪登记，同事去了解求證，她一方面話私人理由，一方面又話回佣金的事，而同事强调回佣沒有問題，但當時未有正式公佈正確佣金，所以免得誤会，而之后劉小姐隨后block 左我同事，希望大家评下理，经纪揾生意已经難，競爭大，仲要回佣，希望密食，点知仲要轉頭揾其他经纪，仲要block whatsapp, 评下理！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/235840_a1c0230fa924d6bc7643ad9b89c8ca94.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F235840_a1c0230fa924d6bc7643ad9b89c8ca94.JPG&h=3c6ad3d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/235840_d1c188791e7158c5920b7f40081d42af.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F235840_d1c188791e7158c5920b7f40081d42af.JPG&h=392a1790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/235841_d0eeba52d2c0c9bf026fb5193a8b33df.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F235841_d0eeba52d2c0c9bf026fb5193a8b33df.JPG&h=ccc9ee4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/235841_2ea8176ecf591257c4023898380e2805.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F235841_2ea8176ecf591257c4023898380e2805.JPG&h=adfd9504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/